  "title": "🤩 Charity Strategy Lead (outdoor sales & marketing)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Entry-Level Role – Perfect for people who no relevant experience</strong></p><p><strong></strong></p><p><strong>Just graduated (or about to)? Looking for your first real job or a career switch? We’ve got you covered.</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p><p>* Learn about the clients products and market their products</p><p>* Have the opportunity to guide new individuals</p><p>* Lead a team</p><p></p><p><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><p>* Positive attitude and eagerness to learn</p><p>* Good communication skills</p><p>* Leadership skills to lead a team</p><p>* Team player who’s also able to work independently</p><p></p><p><strong>Why You’ll Like Working Here</strong></p><p>* Mentorship to help you succeed</p><p>* Room to grow and advance</p><p>* Get paid for your efforts</p><p>* Travel opportunities for expansion or recreational purposes</p><p>* Being part of a supportive team</p><p>* Supporting & inclusive company culture</p><p></p><p><strong>📨 How to Apply</strong></p><p><strong>Contact Justin Yiew at 98371106 on WhatsApp or telegram!We’re excited to meet you!</strong></p>",
